WEBVTT

00:04:00.294 --> 00:04:01.450
Oh my God.

00:04:03.232 --> 00:04:07.056
Not only had my country been attacked,

00:04:07.080 --> 00:04:08.422
but in a flash,

00:04:08.446 --> 00:04:12.352
somebody else's actions
had turned me from a citizen

00:04:12.376 --> 00:04:13.798
to a suspect.

00:04:15.021 --> 00:04:19.958
That same day, we had to drive
across Middle America

00:04:19.982 --> 00:04:23.389
to move to a new city
to start grad school.

00:04:24.908 --> 00:04:26.991
And I remember sitting
in the passenger seat

00:04:27.015 --> 00:04:28.990
as we drove in silence,

00:04:29.871 --> 00:04:32.457
crouched as low as I could go in my seat,